1.2 = LEFT SIDE PANEL SECTION

1.3 = HERO SECTION
1.3.1 Left Hero Text
1.3.1 Right Hero Image

1.4 = MAIN SECTION
1.4.1 ROW 1 - SHOES
1.4.2 ROW 2 - GIRLS TOYS
